<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jennifer Garner put her hard work at the gym on display, as she headed out of the house in a pair of form-fitting black leggings on Friday. </p>

<p>As she enjoyed a walk around her Los Angeles neighborhood with a female pal, the 48-year-old Golden Globe winner dressed to highlight her lean and muscular legs. </p>

<p>Staying cautious of the ongoing coronavirus pandemic, she kept her nose and mouth covered under a white floral face mask. </p>

<p>Athletic: Jennifer Garner put her hard work at the gym on display, as she headed out of the house in a pair of form-fitting black leggings on Friday</p>

<p>The mother-of-three paired her sporty ensemble with a black tank top, a grey baseball cap and blue sneakers. </p>

<p>She opted to tie a white sweater around her waist, which further emphasized her fit physique. </p>

<p>As the duo chatted away on their stroll, they kept some distance between them and appeared in high spirits.  </p>

<p>Fit: As she enjoyed a walk around her Los Angeles neighborhood with a female pal, the 48-year-old Golden Globe winner dressed to highlight her lean and muscular legs</p>

<p>While Garner appeared vigilant about keeping her facial covering on properly, her friend kept her respective mask lowered under her chin. </p>

<p>Her outing comes days after it was reported that the actress felt her ex-boyfriend, John Miller, 'brought her back to life' after the end of her marriage to Ben Affleck. </p>

<p>Garner and Miller dated for two years before calling it quits in early August. </p>

<p>Pals: As the duo chatted away on their stroll, they kept some distance between them and appeared in high spirits </p>

<p>John 'became someone very significant,' proving 'that there were men who could be trusted,' a source told Us Weekly, earlier this week. </p>

<p>The insider noted that he made Jennifer 'feel beautiful, confident and sexy.'</p>

<p>The lovebirds are reportedly still friends following their split, the outlet's source said.</p>

<p>Moving on: Jennifer Garner split with John Miller in early August after two years of dating; seen in 2018</p>

<p>Jennifer and John had conversations about marriage 'but Jen couldn't see herself married to him' and 'couldn't commit.'</p>

<p>The source revealed that 'he wanted to spend the rest of his life with her,' and 'was devastated' since he 'was ready to propose.'</p>

<p>John, who is the CEO of CaliGroup, was previously married to Caroline Campbell; they share two children. </p>

<p>The way they were: 'Jen says John brought her back to life,' according to the source, although 'it just wasn't meant to be;' Jennifer and Ben picture at the 85th Annual Academy Awards on February 24, 2013</p>

<p>An additional source told Us Weekly: 'John and Jen are in similar places in their lives and can relate to raising kids after a divorce,' adding: 'They're on the same page and understand where things stand.'</p>

<p>Jennifer and Ben, 48, in 2004 and married on June 29, 2005, in Turks and Caicos; they announced their separation in June 2015.</p>

<p>They filed for divorce in April 2017 and it was finalized in October 2018; the stars have been co-parenting their children: Violet, 14, Seraphina, 11, and Samuel, eight. </p>
